# prompts/

Empty in this reference plugin. The skill's instructions live entirely in
SKILL.md; no separate prompt fragments are required.

This directory is included so contributors copying the example as a template
have an obvious place to drop skill-internal prompt fragments if their own
skill needs them. Common reasons to use it:

- Long static system-prompt blocks that would bloat SKILL.md.
- Multi-language prompt variants where SKILL.md picks one based on locale.
- Reusable preamble snippets shared across multiple skill modes.

If you do not need any of those, delete this directory in your copy.
